Fiat CEO Says Near 30% Chrysler Stake, Radiocor Says

-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 
2011-04-07T17:54:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/fiat-ceo-says-near-30-chrysler-stake-radiocor-says-correct-.html
(Corrects spelling in headline.)  Fiat SpA (F)  is close to increasing its
stake in Chrysler Group LLC to 30 percent, Chief Executive
Officer  Sergio Marchionne  told reporters today in Bologna,
 Italy , Radiocor said.  Fiat may increase its stake to 30 percent in 30 to 60 days,
Marchionne said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
